;前提對話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.95,0:00:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.72,0:00:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夢總有終點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.13,0:00:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再怎麼快樂的夢也是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.59,0:00:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再怎麼恐怖的夢也是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.41,0:00:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被媽媽從溫暖的被窩裡給搖醒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.82,0:00:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夢便會中斷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.62,0:00:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一如往常的　早晨的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.16,0:00:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是如今…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.55,0:00:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}這個夢是從什麼時候開始　變得沒有終點的呢？

;正文字幕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.95,0:02:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳也差不多哭夠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.79,0:02:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生了什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.35,0:02:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳也說些話啊　亞由亞由
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.10,0:02:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗚咕…　人家才不是亞由亞由啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.47,0:02:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊　妳還能好好說話嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.51,0:02:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳這樣盯著我看　我也不知道要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.33,0:02:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道我長得很像妳失散多年的哥哥之類的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.98,0:02:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我差不多該回去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.31,0:02:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳肚子餓了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.89,0:02:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是肚子在餓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.20,0:02:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.29,0:02:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好　我去買點東西來給妳吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.42,0:02:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼想吃的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.54,0:02:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳沒有什麼喜歡吃的東西嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.82,0:02:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…鯛魚燒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.35,0:03:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鯛魚燒是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.77,0:03:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好　妳在這等我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.81,0:03:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我等你…

;本話標題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.49,0:03:08.99,Title,,0000,0000,0080,,第４話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.49,0:03:08.99,Title,,0000,0000,0050,,假日的奇想曲

Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.93,0:03:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好　妳有乖乖地在這等了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.04,0:03:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你說要我在這裡等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.22,0:03:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好乖　好乖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.25,0:03:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來　一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.82,0:03:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇　好溫暖喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.55,0:03:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為鯛魚燒剛烤好時最好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.87,0:03:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃喔　妳也吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.55,0:04:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…好鹹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.72,0:04:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是妳剛剛眼淚的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.69,0:04:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是　好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.62,0:04:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.74,0:04:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後我也非常地著急
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.48,0:04:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那　妳為什麼哭呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.56,0:04:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊　算了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果妳不想說　我今天就先不問了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.59,0:04:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我差不多該回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.40,0:04:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見啦　亞由亞由
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.60,0:04:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.43,0:04:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…　不叫亞由亞由
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.33,0:04:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.12,0:04:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.24,0:04:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳這樣子我走不了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.22,0:04:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鯛魚燒…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.38,0:05:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還想再吃鯛魚燒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.52,0:05:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳這麼喜歡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.65,0:05:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我再陪妳一起吃好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.63,0:05:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.65,0:05:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那明天一樣的時間　我在車站前的長椅等妳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.25,0:05:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不騙我？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.65,0:05:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不騙妳　我一定會來的！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.19,0:05:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,約好了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.48,0:05:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯　我跟妳約定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.38,0:05:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打勾勾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.97,0:05:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算不打勾勾　我也一樣會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.73,0:05:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗚咕　打勾勾…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.19,0:05:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.88,0:05:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打勾勾了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.65,0:05:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.81,0:05:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.73,0:05:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.48,0:06:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.11,0:06:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯　再見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.75,0:06:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.30,0:06:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,騙子…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.64,0:06:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.77,0:06:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,３
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.15,0:06:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,２
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.56,0:06:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,１
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.88,0:06:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\t(0,500,\fs48\t(1000,2000,\fs24))}０
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.57,0:06:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.40,0:07:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊嗚～　嚇我一大跳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.75,0:07:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.04,0:07:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在幹嘛喔…　那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.32,0:07:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想對我報復　然後失敗了是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.85,0:07:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒、沒那種事啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.95,0:07:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然是怎樣　那個蒟蒻是宵夜嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.42,0:07:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這、這個啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.20,0:07:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒、沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.44,0:07:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那妳給我啃了它
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.01,0:07:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現、現在…？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.62,0:07:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不是正想要吃嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.91,0:07:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊嗚…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.59,0:07:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.74,0:07:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒味道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.09,0:07:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了　大口吞下它啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.46,0:07:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣～　人家肚子已經飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.98,0:07:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蹧蹋食物是會遭天譴的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.94,0:07:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊嗚…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.00,0:07:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.77,0:07:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.21,0:07:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真、真琴她在吃蒟蒻　說是宵夜…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.80,0:07:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蒟蒻？　肚子這麼餓嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.97,0:07:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊嗚…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.30,0:07:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那下來吧　我做點東西給妳吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.08,0:07:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我肚子已經不餓了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.53,0:07:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了對吧　真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.44,0:07:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊嗚…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.04,0:08:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的　擾人清夢也該適可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.06,0:08:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天一定要把這堆整理好才行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.20,0:08:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安　真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.69,0:08:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊嗚…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.96,0:08:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳早上打招呼的方式是「啊嗚」嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.04,0:08:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胸口一直覺得熱熱的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.23,0:08:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰叫妳在半夜還吵著要吃東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.03,0:08:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家才沒有要吃　那是要往祐一的臉上…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.33,0:08:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,往我的臉怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.42,0:08:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊嗚～　嗚～～～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.47,0:08:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你給我等著瞧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.47,0:08:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我出門一下喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.70,0:08:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要去買東西嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.16,0:08:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯　然後名雪忘了帶便當　我正要送去給她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.22,0:09:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她今天好像也去田徑社練習了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.86,0:09:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那由我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.23,0:09:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,田徑社的社長啊…　不知道她會是什麼樣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.40,0:09:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名雪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.92,0:09:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊　祐一～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.34,0:09:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你幫我送來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.63,0:09:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.78,0:09:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這建築物的規模還真不得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.93,0:09:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這間學校很重視社團活動呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.89,0:09:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳很努力嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.06,0:09:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距大會也很近了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.81,0:10:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我該過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.53,0:10:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以稍微參觀一下嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.92,0:10:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯　在角落的話　ＯＫ喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.99,0:10:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你　祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？　香里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.07,0:10:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相澤同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.60,0:10:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在要去社團嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.69,0:10:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.90,0:10:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名雪也好　妳也好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.32,0:10:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明是假日　還真認真啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.23,0:10:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名雪的話是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.33,0:10:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的話　只是不想待在家裡而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.36,0:10:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟父母吵架了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.66,0:10:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.34,0:11:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相澤同學　已經習慣這學校了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.78,0:11:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以才上沒幾天的情況來看　還算可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.28,0:11:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了呢　在教室裡有認識的人在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.54,0:11:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳指名雪嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.27,0:11:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以太讓名雪困擾喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.89,0:11:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了她你才能適應班上　要感謝她才行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.76,0:11:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.01,0:11:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然名雪一副不當一回事的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.66,0:11:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但她有時候也是挺逞強的　要多關心一下喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.32,0:11:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,社團也是每天都練到筋疲力盡為止
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.16,0:11:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來她這麼能睡還有這層原因在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.47,0:11:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是天生的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.11,0:11:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是

Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.48,0:11:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀　祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.38,0:11:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊　秋子阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.62,0:11:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起喔　難得的休息時間還麻煩你這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.06,0:11:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會　小事一樁啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.51,0:12:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秋子阿姨要一個人搬這些的話會很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.92,0:12:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊　有祐一在真是幫了我個大忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.45,0:12:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一君～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.46,0:12:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是祐一君　又見面了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.83,0:12:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.94,0:12:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.72,0:12:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗚咕　又撞到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.87,0:12:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次可不是我的錯囉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.65,0:12:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.27,0:12:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.30,0:12:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊　是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.10,0:12:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是祐一的朋友嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.94,0:12:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我完全不認識這個女生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.14,0:12:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.68,0:12:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗚咕　太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.69,0:12:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.78,0:12:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一君該不會討厭我吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒那回事喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.14,0:12:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔？　妳今天也去吃霸王鯛了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.27,0:12:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦　這是剛剛賣鯛魚燒的伯伯給我的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.81,0:12:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳明明給他添了那麼多麻煩的說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.13,0:12:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是個人好到不行的老伯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.02,0:12:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是活潑的女孩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.16,0:12:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃　請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.05,0:13:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水瀨秋子小姐　是讓我寄住那家人的戶長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.16,0:13:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戶長…是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.08,0:13:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是在家裡最了不起的那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.24,0:13:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊　學到一件事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.59,0:13:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一　也介紹這位給我認識吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.49,0:13:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊　她叫月宮亞由　是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.09,0:13:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請您多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.08,0:13:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦　月宮…亞由？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.25,0:13:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,0:13:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊　沒什麼　是我的錯覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.63,0:13:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一　你接下來要去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.43,0:13:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正打算要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.18,0:13:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搬家的行李也得在今天內整理好才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.45,0:13:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話我也來幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.02,0:13:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳有空嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.02,0:13:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯　而且你昨天也陪我找東西　就當是回禮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.49,0:13:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.60,0:13:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叨擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.86,0:13:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請進
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.21,0:14:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到妳還挺淑女的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.38,0:14:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為妳會像往常那樣一臉撞進去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.20,0:14:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種事人家才不常做啦…呀～！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.18,0:14:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.34,0:14:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.26,0:14:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.23,0:14:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴　出來啦　我替妳介紹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.21,0:14:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.31,0:14:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,澤渡真琴　和我一樣寄住在這家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.85,0:14:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳這樣會讓人家覺得心裡毛毛的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.31,0:14:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少下來打個招呼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.23,0:14:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是月宮亞由　請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.75,0:14:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是澤、澤渡真琴　請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.36,0:14:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,順道一提　妳要不要也來幫我整理行李？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.58,0:15:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦　真琴也要嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.77,0:15:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好歹是在別人家裡吃閒飯的　幫點小忙也不為過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.86,0:15:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊嗚～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.36,0:15:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴　妳還好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.44,0:15:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊嗚…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.40,0:15:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳啊　真的是很沒力氣耶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.33,0:15:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊嗚…　別管我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.26,0:15:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦　這裡就是祐一君的房間啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.20,0:15:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好累　人家沒力了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.17,0:15:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳只不過才搬了一箱而已吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.71,0:15:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的我來搬　妳們把東西拿出來排好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.05,0:15:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什、什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.27,0:15:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要吃嗎？　鯛魚燒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.47,0:15:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.72,0:15:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有點涼掉了　不嫌棄的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.36,0:16:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好甜…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.50,0:16:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不喜歡吃甜的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.05,0:16:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.44,0:16:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的　會胖喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.90,0:16:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.35,0:16:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為很累了　說是等一下再吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.68,0:16:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然三個人同心協力很快就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.30,0:16:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳跟真琴都只是一直把東西翻來覆去而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.02,0:16:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗚咕…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.31,0:16:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是　至少有幫上一點忙吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.73,0:17:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯　多虧妳們　幫了不少忙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.01,0:17:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.76,0:17:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果說要幫忙卻沒派上用場　那我就變騙子了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.15,0:17:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞由　要找的東西找到了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.75,0:17:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不　還沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.60,0:17:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要找的東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.85,0:17:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊　雖然不知道是什麼　但似乎在找很重要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.97,0:17:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為上次祐一幫我一起找　所以今天一方面也是做為回禮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.54,0:17:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊　能早點找到就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.72,0:17:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.29,0:17:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.55,0:17:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.90,0:17:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳一個人回得去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.52,0:17:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家又不是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.66,0:17:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.56,0:17:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原本也想跟真琴打個招呼再走的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.67,0:17:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是在睡午覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.63,0:17:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有機會的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.75,0:17:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.44,0:17:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎隨時再來玩喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.06,0:18:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯　那再見囉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.04,0:18:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.96,0:18:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.79,0:18:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要吃蜂蜜蛋糕？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.37,0:18:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊　妳已經回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.75,0:18:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.98,0:18:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了　祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.52,0:18:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要替我按摩嗎？　不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.10,0:18:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.26,0:18:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那等洗完澡後再麻煩妳囉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.90,0:18:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是按摩的事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.24,0:19:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是來拿借給你的筆記的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.51,0:19:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳的…筆記？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.37,0:19:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是借你了嗎？　因為你說進度比之前的學校要快
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.37,0:19:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.15,0:19:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想起來了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.10,0:19:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就一直放在學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.60,0:19:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦　這樣人家很傷腦筋耶　得要寫作業的說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.86,0:19:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉　明天到學校再還妳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.09,0:19:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.72,0:19:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能就這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.80,0:19:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就醬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.46,0:19:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就說也不是就醬…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.50,0:19:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那妳說要怎麼做才行啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.10,0:19:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才想問你呢　怎麼辦才好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.82,0:19:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天再想吧　今晚早點上床睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.23,0:19:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天就來不及了　祐一沒辦法寫作業也很傷腦筋吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.28,0:19:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是已經超越這些瑣事的男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.65,0:19:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我超越不了　作業沒寫完的話　那老師很嚴的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.20,0:19:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.95,0:19:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫我到學校去把筆記拿回來是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.68,0:20:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是沒有到那種地步啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.47,0:20:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好　我現在就去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.96,0:20:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.56,0:20:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學校門大概沒開喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.29,0:20:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該有些窗子是開的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.70,0:20:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒開的話　我就打破玻璃闖進去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.62,0:20:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.18,0:20:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外面很冷耶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.51,0:20:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係　就一邊慢跑過去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.83,0:20:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.50,0:20:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,香里也特別告誡過我了啊　說是別給妳添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.25,0:20:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起喔　為了我要多跑學校一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.11,0:20:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我自作自受　別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.63,0:20:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這星空還真壯觀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.72,0:21:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來　就快點打道回府吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.91,0:21:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？

;次回預告
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.43,0:23:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.72,0:23:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除魔者
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.59,0:23:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還可以說「你！被退學了！」喔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.70,0:23:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家才不想做那種事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.72,0:23:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除魔者除魔者除魔…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.65,0:23:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秋子小姐很會做菜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.05,0:23:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次嚐嚐特製果醬妳就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.93,0:24:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想吃什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.44,0:24:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一　真的像哥哥一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.11,0:24:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為會被殺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.91,0:24:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳到底是來做啥的啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.20,0:24:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過來

